                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10160" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1518</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">381 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">茶百道上市破发记：资本棋局中的茶饮沉浮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Record of ChaBaiDao&#39;s Post-IPO Break: The Ups and Downs of Tea Beverages in the Capital Chess Game</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">任莉莉，杨若寒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川茶百道实业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO破发；茶饮行业；茶百道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO break；tea beverage industry；ChaBaiDao</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，新茶饮行业快速发展，众多品牌加速资本化进程，茶百道作为头部企业之一，于2024年4月23日登陆港交所，却在上市首日惨遭破发，引发市场广泛关注。为何业绩良好的茶百道会出现IPO破发？其上市选择是否合理？新茶饮企业当下是否适合上市？本案例聚焦茶百道IPO破发事件，系统梳理了茶百道的上市进程、首日破发表现及后续发展态势。通过引导学生运用相关理论对这一事件及后续过程进行深度解析，可助力学生明晰企业IPO破发的多元成因，探究相应的应对策略，并为其他茶饮企业的上市决策提供借鉴。这一过程不仅能帮助学生构建有关IPO及IPO破发的知识体系，更能有效提升其认知、分析和解决企业有关IPO问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the new tea beverage industry has developed rapidly, with numerous brands accelerating their capitalization process. As one of the leading enterprises, Chabaidao was listed on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange on April 23, 2024, but suffered a sharp break on its first day of trading, attracting widespread market attention. Why did Chabaidao, with sound performance, experience an IPO break? Was its decision to go public reasonable? Is it currently suitable for new tea beverage enterprises to list? Focusing on Chabaidao&#39;s IPO break incident, this case systematically sorts out Chabaidao&#39;s listing process, its performance on the first day of the break, and its subsequent development trend. By guiding students to conduct in-depth analysis of this incident and the subsequent process using relevant theories, it can help students clarify the multiple causes of enterprises&#39; IPO breaks, explore corresponding response strategies, and provide references for other tea beverage enterprises&#39; listing decisions. This process can not only help students build a knowledge system related to IPOs and IPO breaks, but also effectively improve their ability to recognize, analyze and solve enterprises&#39; IPO-related problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司金融》、《证券发行与承销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">港股上市条件；IPO破发；企业估值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
